body:
So, after a few matches played as teemo, I noticed quite a distracting thing with the voiceover.

Whenever there&#039;s a teemo on the other team using any skin other than the omega squad teemo (Haven&#039;t met any with that skin on my endeavours, so let&#039;s assume it doesn&#039;t trigger the bug), and you&#039;re playing the teemo as the Legendary skin, quite often the voiceover will play the regular teemo lines like &quot;Never underestimate the scout&#039;s code&quot;. It only happens when issuing movement and attack commands. I am looking forward for a fix because the sound effects are one of the most important aspects of the game and this thing is just annoying.

{{champion:17}} Bring teemo maining back to my life rito please ;w; {{champion:17}}
